title: MBMBaM 550: The Spider-Man Truth
description:
This week, Justin passes judgement on Travis's intro privileges. More importantly though, Justin has a new tool that is finally going to make the show good!


Suggested Talking Points: The Dirty Side of the Shirt, What the Heck?!, Cougar Announcements, The Science Isn't In!

Ways to support Black Lives Matter and find anti-racism resources: https://linktr.ee/blacklivesmatter
